  "commentary": "With SPX at 6787.23 sitting between the flip at 6778 and the massive +52.4B gamma wall at 6800, dealers are in PIN regime and likely selling into this move as we approach their max hedging level. The 20%+ GEX surge with wall_break detection suggests heavy options flow is creating a significant gravitational pull around 6800, where dealers will aggressively sell rallies to hedge their long gamma exposure. Below 6778, the regime would flip and dealers would switch to buying dips, but the current setup favors mean reversion with 6800 acting as strong resistance and 6785-6790 providing intermediate support levels.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to stall and reverse near 6800 with choppy action in the 6785-6795 range.",
